OL,6,FPolice in parts of have been granted
OL,7,Fextra powers to stop and search people
OL,8,Fafter two men in their 20s were
OL,9,Finjured in a knife attack.
OL,11,F11 people have now been arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of attempted murder
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident which happened
OL,14,Fnear Rawnsley Park in at around 4:40am
OL,15,Fon Sunday 9 June.
OL,17,FAll 11 remain in police custody.
OL,19,FTwo men in their 20s were taken to
OL,20,Fhospital with knife wounds, one still
OL,21,Fin a serious condition.
