OL,3,CExtra stop and search powers granted
OL,4,Cafter knife attack in Bristol
OL,6,FSuperintendent of Avon and Somerset
OL,7,FPolice, Lisa Simpson has now granted
OL,8,Fauthority for officers to stop and
OL,9,Fsearch any person or vehicle for a
OL,10,Fweapon near where the incident
OL,11,Fhappened, if they have suspicions they
OL,12,Fmay be carrying weapons.
OL,14,FOfficers are also able to ask people
OL,15,Fto remove face coverings if they have
OL,16,Freason to believe it is being worn to
OL,17,Fconceal their identity.
OL,19,FThe powers will come into force from
OL,20,F7pm tonight (9 June) and will be in
OL,21,Fplace initially for 24 hours.
