OL,3,CExtra stop and search powers granted
OL,4,Cafter knife attack in Bristol
OL,6,FOfficers who are deployed in this way
OL,7,Fhave completed a specific briefing on
OL,8,Fthese powers to ensure they are used
OL,9,Fcorrectly.
OL,11,FSupt Lisa Simpson said: "We do not
OL,12,Funderestimate the concerns of the
OL,13,Flocal community following this recent
OL,14,Fincident of knife crime and serious
OL,15,Fviolence in Bristol.
OL,17,F"It is because of this that we have
OL,18,Fmade the decision to bring in the
OL,19,Fsection 60 powers for our officers.
